  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688272&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688272&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637237\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_traceSets_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f08d6325-3f7a-400e-bcbd-04ec2bdfbe12\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>Defining group memberships allows RenderMan to associate different objects and lights for special effects. For example, you can group a light with objects to prevent them from casting shadows from that specific light or even avoid reflecting something for artistic purposes. <br/>You can achieve some of these effects in post-compositing using <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFB24&amp;title=Light%20Path%20Expressions\" rel=\"nofollow\">Light Path Expressions</a> (LPE), but you can achieve some of these effects globally and during the render. In doing so, your LPE will conform to these choices globally.</p><h2 id=\"TraceSetsEditor-Why?\">Why?</h2><p>Trace sets are valuable for tweaking images artistically. Many images you see have been altered for the public. Blemishes get removed, distracting patterns get painted out, and even bad highlights and composition gets &quot;fixed&quot; based on art direction. <br/><br/>When rendering these same rules apply. You may have had an art director tell you to remove a distracting shadow from off-screen or erase a reflection from something too bright or obscuring. In some cases this is simple, but at other times you need to remove the offending effect from just a single object or maybe a collection. <br/><br/>Trace Sets are where you go to make this happen!</p><h2 id=\"TraceSetsEditor-UsingTheTraceSetsEditor\">Using The Trace Sets Editor</h2><p>To open the trace sets editor in Blender, go to the scene properties and click the Trace Sets Editor button. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1367\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=62\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"62\" data-width=\"917\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637249\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_traceSets_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"28ad03ac-f6ca-4cbd-a6b4-d19a8abf4477\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=62 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderManForBlender_traceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=62 1x\"></span><p>You can also open it from the object context menu in the viewport.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=596&amp;height=161\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"161\" data-width=\"596\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637201\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_open2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"78ee1000-32e7-4ba1-85bc-6aa0cf2a3869\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=596&amp;height=161 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=596&amp;height=161 1x\"></span><p /><p>When you first open the editor, it should be empty like this:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=134\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_editor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"134\" data-width=\"511\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637204\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_editor1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3b7ec24e-5197-4e29-b484-dd7daa866fca\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=134 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=134 1x\"></span><p>To add a new trace set, click the + button on the right. A default name for the trace set will be automatically used. <br/>Clicking on the - button will remove the selected trace set.<br/><br/></p><p>Next, select the objects you want to add to the current trace set from the drop-down menu. You can also do a filter search, by clicking on the filter funnel button on the left.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=312\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_editor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"312\" data-width=\"511\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637207\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_editor2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7073b436-fd2f-4493-aeb1-8a1cbd9105c0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=312 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=511&amp;height=312 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=517&amp;height=338\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_editor3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"338\" data-width=\"517\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637210\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_editor3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f126dcb7-6d28-4ca6-a1ad-40bf4220f6e2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=517&amp;height=338 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=517&amp;height=338 1x\"></span><p /><p>The added object will be placed in the list at the bottom. <br/>Clicking on the - button next to the name of the object will remove the object from the currently selected trace set.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"811\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687667&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=514&amp;height=312\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_editor4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687667&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"312\" data-width=\"514\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637213\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_editor4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86f4bee2-2732-483e-8f77-f0dddbaccee2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687667&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=514&amp;height=312 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_editor4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687667&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=514&amp;height=312 1x\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"TraceSetsEditor-TheInvisibleToySoldier\">The Invisible Toy Soldier</h2><p>To demonstrate the use of the trace sets editor, here's a render from a simple scene.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637240\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7d8ec55f-e936-4aeb-bb01-bf87499af33f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1368&amp;height=768 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=384 1x\"></span><p>For this scene, let's add the toy soldier to a trace set called &quot;vampire&quot;</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=515&amp;height=332\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_example1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"332\" data-width=\"515\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637219\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_example1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"df7ccead-7b0e-4cf1-9e1b-1cac9c495b84\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=515&amp;height=332 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=515&amp;height=332 1x\"></span><p>Now, on the chrome ball object, go to the object properties, and look under the Ray Tracing panel. Add the &quot;vampire&quot; trace set to the Reflect Exclude Subset.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=448&amp;height=556\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/trace_sets_example2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"556\" data-width=\"448\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637222\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"trace_sets_example2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"65068519-d10f-4903-991d-baa544ea7c51\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=448&amp;height=556 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637184/trace_sets_example2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687885&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=448&amp;height=556 1x\"></span><p>If we now render the scene, this should be the result:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637243\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5069069b-ae59-4771-92cf-958a09b33178\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>We can also see the cutout of the soldier in the chrome ball.  This is due to the fact that the soldier is still visible to transmission (shadow) rays from the chrome ball's perspective. We can remove this by also adding the 'invisible' set to the &quot;Shadow Exclude Subset&quot; on the chrome ball object.<br/><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637184/RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432688470&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637246\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_TraceSets_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637184\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"73a23e0d-f535-4d6c-bd34-15406f821daf\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p>"
    }
  },
